{"tid":1249731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（文宣）係巴士落廣告宣傳反送中？","createTime":"2019-06-21T20:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T16:18:44.000Z","uid":54303,"like":62,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"735df63a786766efd46df9ff2b2a2ce0de453fdc","tid":1249731,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qApis2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqApis2f.png&h=3bb6f061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翻譯：<br />\n我地每星期送左3億5千萬比歐盟洗<br />\n不如留黎改善醫療系統啦 &mdash; 投脫歐<br />\n<br />\n我地要話番事<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n巴士既好處係可以接觸到唔太識上網既老一輩/師奶<br />\n而且不斷既全方位宣傳轟炸 <br />\n會令市民對我方既主張潛移默化地認同<br />\n成本方面五萬一架左右 我相信泛民+連登一定輕鬆夠錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkbus.fandom.com/wiki/巴士車身廣告\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkbus.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2F%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%BB%8A%E8%BA%AB%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0Pmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=9a1a576d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkbus.fandom.com/wiki/巴士車身廣告</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n值得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哂鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b73f5997b9f2750cdf7437ffb69a156988de654","tid":1249731,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:08:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5c29c0148785e71203cbd0ac6ea4a3ffb22e202","tid":1249731,"uid":78947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:09:04.000Z","msg":"政治野多數唔做你生意"},{"pid":"e1701550ae3619070e58fcca63dc502f00597da4","tid":1249731,"uid":87735,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:13:18.000Z","msg":"不如自己整易拉架可能仲實際啲 <br />\n不過注意食環會拉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1BwN7h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna